{"id":91965,"title":"[Treatment of cervical esophageal perforation].","abstract":"To investigate the repair of cervical esophageal perforation using cervical muscle flap and provide a new material of esophageal perforation repair.To report 12 cases of cervical esophageal perforation among which 8 cases was repaired using cervical muscle flap.100% success rate of surgical repair was observed with all 12 cases. No case of recurrence or esophageal stricture occurred by follow-up six months to 10 years.Traumatic cervical esophageal perforation easily had serious complications, with high mortality rates and the prognosis was poor. Early intervention of surgical repair could improve the survival rate of patients.","date":"2014-01-27","categories":"Wounds and Injuries","split":"test","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24459923","annotations":[{"name":"Stenosis","weight":0.802802,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stenosis"},{"name":"Complication (medicine)","weight":0.787846,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Complication_(medicine)"},{"name":"Mortality rate","weight":0.734333,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mortality_rate"},{"name":"Prognosis","weight":0.73221,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prognosis"},{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.684152,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Esophagus","weight":0.678312,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esophagus"},{"name":"Trauma (medicine)","weight":0.654651,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trauma_(medicine)"},{"name":"Cervical vertebrae","weight":0.566785,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cervical_vertebrae"},{"name":"Death","weight":0.430036,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Death"},{"name":"Muscle","weight":0.387715,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Muscle"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.341581,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"